## Visualization (PC or Mac)

```java

> if (!requireNamespace("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE)) install.packages("BiocManager")

> BiocManager::install("igvR")

> library(SplitFusion)

> bam2igv(bamfile = "Lib001.EML4_intronic---ALK_exon20.bam")


```

